Select values

This function extract values

select_values(x)

Arguments

x
a list

Examples

library(jsonlite)
library(magrittr)
"bis-pp-ls-q-au" %>%
 paste0(widukind_api, "series/", .) %>%
 fromJSON() %>%
 select_data() %>%
 select_values()
